This paper proposes a new boosting algorithm that improves the training phase efficiency while maintaining the formal guarantees of the original AdaBoost algorithm. The paper includes theoretical derivations and experiments with synthetic and real datasets. Based on this information, the most likely sub-categories are machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), and cryptography and security (cs.CR).
